taiwan trade surplu widen in first quarter taiwan 's trade surplu widen to 4.18 billion u.s. dlr in the first quarter of 1987 from 3.05 billion a year ago , the govern statist depart said . first quarter export rose to 11.25 billion u.s. dlr from 8.38 billion in the same period in 1986. import rose to 7.08 billion from 5.33 billion last year . the march trade surplu wa 1.45 billion dlr compar with 1.32 billion in februari and 1.02 billion in march 1986. export rose to 4.07 billion u.s. dlr from 3.85 billion in februari and 2.99 billion in march last year . import were 2.61 billion dlr against 2.53 billion in februari and 1.96 billion in march 1986 .